data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Stone Oak area! This stunning property offers over 3,200 sq. ft. of luxurious living space, featuring 4 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 baths. With 3 living areas, there's plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment. Prepare to be amazed by the double ovens, gas cooking range, and ample counter space that will inspire your culinary creations. Great Office/Study space, formal dining room as well as a breakfast room all located downstairs!  Upstairs features a large Game room/Loft, Laundry room and all 4 bedrooms.  Master Suite has high ceilings with an amazing Master Bathroom and large walk-in closet! Master Bathroom has 2 separate vanities, separate shower and jetted jacuzzi tub.  Exterior features 4 sides stone and brick, covered patio and deck, sprinkler system and mature trees.  Upgrades include: New carpet throughout, state of the art new Water Softener, both HVAC units have been replaced in the last yr, roof was replaced in 2020 and double ovens replaced in the last year. Location is amazing!  Easy commute to 281, Loop 1604, Camp Bullis, shopping and restaurants.
